            <a:r>
              <a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="3200" b="1" dirty="0"/>
              <a:t>1 drone covers 12 km&#xB2; at ~20% the cost of equivalent ground patrol. Fully autonomous &#x2014; zero pilot required for dispatch.</a:t>
            </a:r>
